  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Experimental Summoning Technology",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "试验召唤技术",
    "TraditionalChinese": "實驗召喚技術"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "The result of Nada's research into unusual patterns detected in the stories of the <TRANS_TRA>Gek<>, <TRANS_EXP>Korvax<>, and <TRANS_WAR>Vy'keen<>.<br><br>The beacon broadcasts a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">signal echo</span> attuned to the shift <span class=\"name name-special\">historiographical flux</span> mapped by Nada's Traveller companions.<br><br>Specialist Polo is unwilling to predict the results of the broadcast.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "纳达对<TRANS_TRA>吉克<>、<TRANS_EXP>科尔瓦克斯<>和<TRANS_WAR>维吉恩<>故事中不寻常的模式的研究结果。<br><br>该信标广播了一个<span class=\"name name-stellar\">信号回音</span>，与纳达的旅行者同伴绘制的<span class=\"name name-special\">史学波动</span>变化相适应。<br><br>保罗专家不愿意预测广播的结果。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "納達對<TRANS_TRA>吉客族<>、<TRANS_EXP>科瓦族<>和<TRANS_WAR>維金族<>故事中偵測到的異常模式進行研究，這是他取得的成果。<br><br>信標會廣播一道經過調整的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">訊號回波</span>，可偵測到納達的旅行者同伴定位到的<span class=\"name name-special\">史學史通量</span>偏移。<br><br>專家波羅不願意預測廣播的結果。"
  },
